=== settings_demo ===
: Settings Menu

In the `settings` menu above, you will find:

> Theme switcher (light/dark/auto)
> Font switcher, including accessibility options such as dyslexia-friendly font, font sizing and spacing options
> Audio controls (if the story contains audio)
> Animation control
> Enable/disable the autosave feature

You can open the settings menu with `ctrl`+`,` (`cmd`+`,` on Mac) and close it with `esc`.

